# Phase 2: Remove CG, switch to pure AT, collect RDF
unfix bm
unfix integrate
delete_atoms group cg_atoms
Deleted 3000 atoms, new total = 6000

# Types 1,2 deleted but LAMMPS keeps type metadata — dummy coeffs needed.
pair_style lj/cut 14.00
pair_modify shift yes
pair_coeff * * 0.1 3.5
pair_coeff 3 3 0.207266 3.748000
pair_coeff 3 4 0.156387 3.826500
pair_coeff 4 4 0.117997 3.905000

bond_style harmonic
bond_coeff 1 800.000883 1.530000
bond_coeff 2 800.000883 1.530000
bond_coeff 3 800.000883 1.530000
bond_coeff 4 800.000883 1.530000

angle_style harmonic
angle_coeff 1 126.673180 111.0000

special_bonds lj 0.0 0.0 0.0 coul 0.0 0.0 0.0

group at_atoms type 3 4
6000 atoms in group at_atoms

fix nve_all at_atoms nve

neigh_modify delay 0 every 1 check yes
timestep 1.00
thermo 50

run 100
